First, to start dealing with VK API using Node.js, you have to install the needed package by running this command: 

```bash
npm install vk-io
```

Then, you need to write Node.js script like the following to get the list of wall posts from VK API:

```javascript
const VK = require('vk-io');
const vk = new VK({
    token: 'YOUR_TOKEN'
});

